{"id":137894,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graveson","text":"Graveson is a commune of 3,836 people (2008). It is found in the region Provence-Alpes-C\u00F4te d'Azur in the Bouches-du-Rh\u00F4ne department in the south of France.\nThe village is very attractive for holidaymakers, because it is located between Arles and Avignon. Neighbour villages are Ch\u00E2teaurenard, Maillane and Rognonas.\nGraveson is birthplace of the painter Auguste Chabaud.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Communes_of_France","surface_form":"commune","offset":14},{"uri":"2008","surface_form":"2008","offset":39},{"uri":"Regions_of_France","surface_form":"region","offset":65},{"uri":"Provence-Alpes-C%C3%B4te_d%27Azur","surface_form":"Provence-Alpes-C\u00F4te d'Azur","offset":72},{"uri":"Bouches-du-Rh%C3%B4ne","surface_form":"Bouches-du-Rh\u00F4ne","offset":106},{"uri":"Departments_of_France","surface_form":"department","offset":123},{"uri":"France","surface_form":"France","offset":150},{"uri":"Arles","surface_form":"Arles","offset":238},{"uri":"Avignon","surface_form":"Avignon","offset":248},{"uri":"Ch%C3%A2teaurenard","surface_form":"Ch\u00E2teaurenard","offset":280},{"uri":"Maillane","surface_form":"Maillane","offset":295},{"uri":"Rognonas","surface_form":"Rognonas","offset":308},{"uri":"Auguste_Chabaud","surface_form":"Auguste Chabaud","offset":356}]}